up staircase very quick-quick.

rows.label: tlk400802_msg0003

country have some child like that.

rows.label: tlk400802_msg0004
rows.name:
Superbia, Invidia, even Acedia.
Gap of rich and poor exist everywhere.

rows.label: tlk400802_msg0006

...Oh, friends chasing after boy to
get back stolen thing?

rows.label: tlk400802_msg0007
rows.name:
*sigh* Should always keep valuables
carefully secure to body when travel!

rows.label: tlk400802_msg0008
rows.name: Yeah... I'll be more careful in future.
